location.fullValue: Carbondale Plan, Manor at Stoney Creek

data.description: NEW ROOF - Exceptional TRUE ranch has been completely updated/upgraded! Recent exterior paint, lush and established lawn and landscape. Step through front door to find open floor plan, entry has new tile floor. Carpet throughout main level is about 3 yrs old, upgraded carpet & pad. Great room has vaulted ceiling, corner fireplace is gas with new tile surround. Fresh interior paint. Updated kitchen has white cabinets, black stainless appliances - range has double oven, top of the lie refrigerator. Wood floors and granite counters, huge walk-in pantry! Lovely dining area has large windows new sliding glass door, vaulted ceiling. Laundry room off kitchen. Primary suite is at back corner of house. Spacious bedroom, huge walk-in closet and luxury bath. Updated bathroom has double vanity, new tile floor, tile surround at jetted tub, large custom shower is fully tiled, zero entry, glass slab walls, niche in tiled wall & dual head Delta fixture. 2 additional bedrooms share hall bath with updated tile floor, tile to the ceiling around the shower/tub. Entire home has updated light fixtures & ceiling fans. All plumbing fixtures updated with top of the line Delta. Both bathrooms have new single piece toilets. AC replaced 2022, furnace replaced 3 months ago, hot water heater 2 months ago. Kitchen appliances replaced around 2019. Oversized garage has workbench & cabinets for storage. Great outdoor living space on patio. Incredible backyard. Landscape has stone edging, established plantings. Neighbors have fences. Community offers multiple pools, play areas, sand volleyball, walking trails & clubhouse. Buyer canceled after inspection, Seller has made several improvements since inspection, reports, receipts available in Supplements
